DESCRIPTION:Discover the ancient art of Kalamkari with master artist K. Siva Prasad Reddy\, in this hands-on workshop presented by MeMeraki. Join us to celebrate the closing weekend of Chay Reds\, Ferrous Black  and immerse yourself in the vibrant tradition of this art form.  Learn the basics of Kalamkari motifs\, practice sketching and painting with traditional bamboo pens\, and create your own unique piece.  \n\nSiva Prasad Reddy will guide you through the process\, from initial sketches to the final vibrant colours\, including a demonstration of the crucial boiling technique.  He will also share insights on how to recognise authentic Kalamkari and offer tips for continued practice.  The workshop ends with a Q&amp\;A session with the artist.\n\nImage credits: Krishna with Cows Kalamkari Painting by Siva Reddy\n\n
DTEND:20250301T083000Z
